---
// 点歌系统 - 全屏播放页面
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>点歌系统 | 咸中广播</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            height: 100vh;
            overflow: hidden;
            background-color: #0a1929;
        }
        .back-btn {
            position: fixed;
            top: 20px;
            left: 20px;
            z-index: 1000;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
            backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
            color: white;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
            font-size: 14px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .back-btn:hover {
            background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.8);
        }
        .voicehub-container {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100vh;
            border: none;
        }
        .loading {
            position: fixed;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            color: #b8d0e0;
            font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
            z-index: 999;
            background: rgba(10, 25, 41, 0.9);
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <a href="/voicehub" class="back-btn">← 返回导航</a>
    <div class="loading" id="loading">🎵 加载点歌系统...</div>
    <iframe 
        src="https://245959623.xyz" 
        class="voicehub-container"
        onload="document.getElementById('loading').style.display = 'none'"
        title="VoiceHub 点歌系统"
    ></iframe>
</body>
</html>
